    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a machine; it's a vessel for memories yet to be made. Imagine yourself behind the wheel as the sun dips below the horizon, the engine humming a low, rhythmic melody that resonates in your chest. Every curve in the leather and every polished line of its body tells a story of sun-drenched coastal drives and moonlit escapes. It possesses a soulful character that modern cars simply can't replicate\u2014a gentle patina of adventure that speaks to a life well-lived and a future full of possibility. This car doesn't just take you from point A to point B; it invites you to fall in love with the journey all over again.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Experience the perfect synergy of performance and reliability with this meticulously maintained professional-grade vehicle. Boasting a clean history and a robust service record, this car has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for safety and comfort. With its refined interior and smooth handling, it represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver seeking quality without compromise. This is a road-ready investment that delivers both confidence and prestige.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
