      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my faithful companion and still drives like a dream\u2014there's honestly nothing like the way she handles the open road. She\u2019s been kept clean and loved, and while she has a few tiny 'beauty marks' from our adventures together, she\u2019s in wonderful shape and ready to make some new memories with you. I\u2019ve always stayed on top of the maintenance because I believe a car this fun deserves the best care. Come by, have a coffee, and take her for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019ll fall in love just like I did!",
      "price": 34500.0,
