      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously dialed-in specimen featuring a high-revving power plant with exceptional compression across all cylinders. I\u2019ve ensured the drivetrain remains tight, with crisp gear engagement and a chatter-free limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry has been optimized for neutral turn-in, utilizing upgraded polyurethane bushings to eliminate deflection under lateral load. Recent service includes a full cooling system overhaul and a high-temp brake fluid flush. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a dedicated driver\u2019s car, the mechanical integrity is beyond reproach, offering a visceral, linear power delivery that modern, over-assisted platforms simply cannot replicate. This is a robust, enthusiast-owned example optimized for peak kinetic response.",
